comments.body: Quote from: Kryptowerk on March 22, 2023, 07:24:52 PMYeah, I noticed many / most (?) CI coins tend to have these tarnishes after a while. Is it the capsules that come originally with them or something on the coin / minting process?I wouldn't even consider it an impairment, since it's so common with CIs.Pretty sure it's just natural as air-tites are never truly "air-tite" ofc....
